productReviews.reviewText: I saw one of these in Algeria and I bought one.
heard about this on instrumental country radio, decided to give it a try.
This Ramp works too well. It nonchalantly improves my baseball by a lot.
My co-worker Delton has one of these. He says it looks slender.
The box this comes in is 5 kilometer by 6 meter and weights 20 ounce!
